      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the relay. The inspection method is the same for each relay. There shall be continuity between No. 3 and No. 5 terminals and between No. 1 and No. 4 terminals and no continuity between No. 1 and No. 2 terminals."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
